User defined constructor to initilize class level variables with user provided values.

Parameters:
id - - unique value calculated or enter zero if new property.
legalDescription - - property description of max. 20 characters.
address - - property address of max. 80 characters.
quadrant - - city location with valid entries NE,NW,SE,SW.
zone - - applied zoning with valid entries R1,R2,R3,R4,I1,I2,I3,I4.
askingPrice - - price property is listed for.
comments - - general comments on the property.
area - - area of property in square metres.
bathrooms - - number of bathrooms respresented as #.0 or #.5.
bedrooms - - number of bedrooms located in home.
garage - - a value of 'a', 'd' or 'n' representing attached, detached or no garage. 1127V4712-24;639 Royal Crest Place;NW;R2;389591.09;Lots of space;4160.8;1.0;4;D
